name: Ml-dedup
body:
### ML-DeDup.
This is a Dedup utility for use with MarkLogic
It will scan through all the files in the current directory
Identify duplicates based on 
```
md = MessageDigest.getInstance("SHA-512");
```
Move the duplicates to a new directory named 'Duplicates'

```
place the jar file in the desired directory
double click the jar
```
note: Don't delete this file! It's used internally to help with page regeneration.
